trans-unit.source: Represents a base class for design-time tools, not derived from <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"></xref>, that provide smart tag or designer verb capabilities.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en basklass för designtid verktyg, inte har härletts från <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner"> </xref>, som tillhandahåller smarta etiketter eller designer verb funktioner.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner> class provides the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Verbs%2A> properties to query for the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb> collections, respectively.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>klassen innehåller den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A>och <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Verbs%2A>Egenskaper för att fråga efter den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>och <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb>samlingar, respektive.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.Verbs%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.ActionLists%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner>

trans-unit.source: However, if a design-time tool author decides not to derive from this class, the DesignerCommandSet class represents an alternative base class to provide this functionality.
trans-unit.target: Om en designläge verktyget författare inte beslutar att härledas från den här klassen representerar klassen DesignerCommandSet ett alternativt basklass med den här funktionen.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerCommandSet class contains only three members, described in the following table.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerCommandSet innehåller endast tre medlemmar som beskrivs i följande tabell.

trans-unit.source: |Public member|Description| |-------------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>|Returns the collection of either the smart tags or designer verbs associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: | Offentlig medlem | Beskrivning | |-------------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>| Returnerar den smarta etiketter eller designer verb som är associerade med komponenten utformad.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base implementation returns `null`.| |<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>|Gets the collection of all the smart tags associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Basimplementationen returnerar `null`. | | <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>| Hämtar insamling av alla smarta etiketter som är associerade med den utformad.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>.| |<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>|Gets the collection of all the designer verbs associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Den grundläggande implementeringen anropar bara <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>. | | <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>| Hämtar insamling av alla designer verb som är associerade med den utformad.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>.| A DesignerCommandSet should be added as a site-specific service.
trans-unit.target: Den grundläggande implementeringen anropar bara <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>. | En DesignerCommandSet ska läggas till som en tjänst som platsspecifika.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: Externally, a service of this type should first be queried to discover smart tag and designer verb functionality.
trans-unit.target: Externt, efterfrågas en tjänst av den här typen först för att identifiera smarta etiketter och designer verb funktioner.

trans-unit.source: If this service is not found, then the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property should be used instead.
trans-unit.target: Om den här tjänsten inte kan hittas, kommer <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen ska användas i stället.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: This procedure provides a path for backwards compatibility.
trans-unit.target: Den här proceduren ger en sökväg för kompatibilitet bakåt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Because this base class contains no state, the default constructor does nothing.
trans-unit.target: Eftersom den här basklass innehåller inget tillstånd, ingenting Standardkonstruktorn.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of all the smart tags associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar insamling av alla smarta etiketter som är associerade med den utformad.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A> with the string parameter "ActionLists".
trans-unit.target: Anropar bara Basimplementationen <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>med strängparametern "ActionLists".</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> that contains the smart tags for the associated designed component.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> som innehåller smarta etiketter för den associerade utformad komponenten.

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of command objects.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar en mängd med kommandoobjekt.

trans-unit.source: Although the base implementation always returns `null`, the overridden version supplied by the programmer should return a collection of command objects of the type described by `name`.
trans-unit.target: Även om den grundläggande implementeringen alltid returnerar `null`, den version tillhandahålls av programmet ska returnera en samling kommandoobjekt av typen som beskrivs av `name`.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A> properties specify the following values and meanings for this parameter.
trans-unit.target: Den grundläggande implementeringen av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>och <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A>Egenskaper anger du följande värden och innebörd för den här parametern.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.ActionLists%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.Verbs%2A>

trans-unit.source: |String|Meaning| |------------|-------------| |"ActionLists"|Return a collection of all the smart tags associated with the component.| |"Verbs"|Return a collection of all the designer verbs associated with the component.|
trans-unit.target: | Sträng | Vilket innebär att | |------------|-------------| |" ActionLists "| Returnera en samling med alla smarta etiketter som är associerade med komponenten. | |" Verb "| Returnera en samling med alla designer verb som är associerade med komponenten. |

trans-unit.source: The type of collection to return, indicating either a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> or a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Typ av samling för att returnera, visar antingen en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A collection that contains the specified type—either <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> or <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb"></xref>—of command objects.
trans-unit.target: En samling som innehåller den angivna typen – antingen <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerb"> </xref>– kommandot objekt.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation always returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar alltid Basimplementationen <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of all the designer verbs associated with the designed component.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar insamling av alla designer verb som är associerade med den utformad.

trans-unit.source: The base implementation simply calls <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A> with the string parameter "Verbs".
trans-unit.target: Anropar bara Basimplementationen <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>med strängparametern "Verb".</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerCommandSet.GetCommands%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"></xref> that contains the designer verbs for the associated designed component.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerVerbCollection"> </xref> som innehåller designer verb för den associerade utformad komponenten.
